snippet.title: Barkour - Official Reveal Trailer | gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Barkour, the latest game from Bee Simulator developer Varsav Studios, is, to quote the team, "an action/stealth game where you take on the role of a tail-wagging canine 009 agent, unleashed by a secret organization to fight evil in a world that that's anything but ruff and serious."

#IGN #Gaming
